<F P=102>  AU1703201894 Sofia BTA in English 1955 GMT 17 Mar 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU1703201894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia BTA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ivaylovgrad, March 19 (BTA) -- Late last night the 
police in Ivaylovgrad (in southern Bulgaria, near the border 
with Greece), detained two diplomats from the French Embassy in 
Bulgaria. Ivaylovgrad falls in the border zone and the two 
diplomats' presence there without the permission of Bulgaria's 
Foreign Ministry is a gross violation of border regulations. 
  The police do not know how the two diplomats reached 
Ivaylovgrad unimpeded. A protocol was drawn up and they left 
for Sofia. 

