<F P=102>  AU2203123094 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1100 GMT 22 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2203123094 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The first aircraft landed at Tuzla airport at 0935 
this morning, carrying 22 metric tons of food, medicine, and 
seeds, and marking the airport's official opening for the 
reception of humanitarian aid. 
