were greeted by Stjepan Kljuic, member of the Bosnia-Herzegovina 
Presidency, General Rasim Delic, commander of the General Staff 
of the Bosnia-Herzegovina Armed Forces, Salih Kulenovic, 
coordinating minister for the Tuzla- Drina region, and 
representatives of the Tuzla district and commune. 

