<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "New Arrests Over Illegal Possession </F>
of Arms"] 
  [Text] According to the announcement of the Municipal 
court in Tetovo, four people have been arrested in the past few 
days, all of Albanian nationality, "due to the founded suspicion 
of committing the criminal act illegal possession of firearms." 
  The Court says that a "larger quantity of automatic guns and 
ammunition" was discovered on the people. 
  Due to these arrests, yesterday's regular session of the 
Tetovo Local Assembly war interrupted in the morning hours, only 
to continue at seven o'clock in the evening, with the presence 
of the Tetovo chief of police, who informed the Assembly about 
the arrests. 
  The session of the Assembly was held behind closed doors. 

