<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Arrest of Albanians -- Political </F>
Case"] 
  [Text] In reference to the latest arrests of Albanian 
citizens, the Albanian People's Democratic Party appealed to all 
government bodies to order an urgent release of all citizens 
imprisoned in this political and fabricated process. 
  They warn the government has an obligation to treat this 
case 
in the same way it did similar attempts by certain Macedonians 
to organise themselves. Otherwise, they say the Macedonian 
Government takes on a responsibility for possible worsening of 
the situation in the country, which is something Macedonia 
[FYROM -- The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia] needs the 
least at the moment. 

